  docs/RELEASE-MANAGEMENT.md,project,Operator and recovery documentation
close_reason: "Change-aware npm release automation, pm-generated lossless changelog ownership, Bun consumer verification, credentials, tests, and operator documentation are complete."
body: "Deliver a scheduled and manually testable release pipeline that skips when no commits exist after the latest release tag, computes the YYYY.M.D[-N] version, regenerates the full changelog from pm items, runs release gates, commits and tags safely, publishes to the npm registry, and proves both Node and Bun consumer execution. Preserve every fact currently present in CHANGELOG.md by backfilling missing pm items before generator ownership begins."
